de.must.appletserver
Class DataPropertyAdministration

java.lang.Object
  de.must.appletserver.RemoteUserInterface
      de.must.appletserver.PropertyAdministration
          de.must.appletserver.DataPropertyAdministration
All Implemented Interfaces:
AppletTalker, Remotable, RemotableControler
public abstract class DataPropertyAdministration
extends PropertyAdministration

Frame-like container to enclose input-output fields like text fields with database field association and controlling load and save actions. Used for property administration of a single database record. It is meant to contain several storables like e.g. DataTextField
